description: A guy is suing Disney because he feels like they stole his song, a Capital One ad had all the past Taylor Swift versions in it, Al B Sure! was in a coma for 2 months, Corey Taylor is writing a novel, there is rain in the forecast, the World Series is tied up, the time change is Saturday night, we vote on Tuesday, 25 percent is becoming the standard tip, Miller Light is going to sell tree keg stands, sometimes you need the dark to see the light, childhood friends reconnected on Facebook and love bloomed, and Vinnie reads your texts!
